            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": {
                "text": "Running alongside our 'States of Mind' exhibition, this project was a way to record and share people’s stories of what happens when they're asleep. We collected the stories and the best ones were sewn into a quilt by our visitors. You can get a sense of the process in the gallery below. We have also kept a record of the stories for our archive.",
                "spans": [
                  {
                    "start": 23,
                    "end": 37,
                    "type": "hyperlink",
                    "data": {
                      "link_type": "Web",
                      "url": "https://wellcomecollection.org/exhibitions/states-mind-tracing-edges-consciousness"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": {
                "text": "Once completed and photographed, the quilt was donated to St Mungo's. The digital version of the quilt acts as both a legacy of this project, as well as a way for people to explore the beautiful contributions our visitors have made whilst getting a sense of the range of sleep experiences we gathered. ",
                "spans": [
                  {
                    "start": 58,
                    "end": 68,
                    "type": "hyperlink",
                    "data": {
                      "link_type": "Web",
                      "url": "http://www.mungos.org/"
                    }
                  }
                ]
